{"parse":{"title":"Shadowmoon Valley","pageid":26989,"wikitext":{"*":":''Were you looking for the [[Draenor]] zone named [[Shadowmoon Valley (Draenor)|Shadowmoon Valley]]?''\n{{Infobox zone\n|ss=Shadowmoon Valley concept.jpg\n|ruler=[[Illidan Stormrage]]\n|pop=Unknown\n|affiliation=[[Illidari]]<br/>[[Sha'tar]]\n|capital=[[Black Temple]]\n|name=Shadowmoon Valley\n|races={{Race|Demon}}<br />{{Race|Fel orc}}<br />{{Race|Naga }}<br />{{Race|Blood elf}}<br />{{Race|Night elf }}<br />{{Race|Draenei}}<br />{{Race|Orc}}<br />{{Race|Wildhammer Dwarf }}<br />{{Race|Netherwing Dragonflight }}<br />{{Race|Felblood Elf }}\n|major=[[Wildhammer Stronghold]]<br />[[Legion Hold]]<br />[[Shadowmoon Village]]<br />[[Dragonmaw Fortress]]\n|loc=Southeastern [[Outland]]\n|level=Scalable 67-80\n}}\n'''Shadowmoon Valley''' is found in southeastern [[Outland]], east of [[Terokkar Forest]]. It is the location of the [[Black Temple]] (where {{npc||Illidan Stormrage}} once resided), and also houses a dwarven settlement named after (and led by) {{npc||Kurdran Wildhammer}}, as well as the prison where Illidan's former jailor, {{npc||Maiev Shadowsong}}, is held captive.\n\n== History ==\n[[File:Shadowmoonvalley.jpg|thumb|A view of the [[Hand of Gul'dan]]]]\nIn addition to being the location of the [[Black Temple]], the region gave name to {{npc||Ner'zhul}}'s [[Shadowmoon Clan]], who once had their holdings there. Prior to destruction of [[Draenor]], the north shore of the region was known as the Skeletal Coast.\n\nWorldofwarcraft.com says the following about the Shadowmoon Valley:\n\n''This valley is a grim spectacle of demonic magic run amok. Day and night, molten fel energy erupts from the land and lights the sky with bilious green flame. To the east lies the Black Temple, Illidan Stormrage's seat of power. With the Dark Portal reopened, Illidan and his allies struggle to hold off Legion reinforcements and keep all other Outland portals closed.''\n\n== Geography ==\nShadowmoon Valley used to be an idyllic forest shrouded by eternal night. Upon Gul'dan's creation of a huge volcano with his demonic powers, much of the area was turned into a barren wasteland of rock and ash, with little vegetation. Like the rest of Outland, Shadowmoon Valley was further torn asunder during the destruction of Draenor by the countless portals created by [[Ner'zhul]]. This fragmented the zone, stripping away several sections of former shoreline and turning the former island of [[Darktide Roost]] into a massive floating outcrop, which would eventually become [[Netherwing Ledge]]. The [[Hand of Gul'dan]], the volcano which Gul'dan created, dominates the center of the region, from which green lava imbued by Fel energy erupts constantly.\n\nThe region was the ancient home of the Shadowmoon clan, before the betrayal of Gul'dan.\n\nThe Alliance and Horde each have a settlement here, as do the [[Aldor]] and [[Scryers]].\n\nThe valley contains one raid instance, the [[Black Temple]] (the ruins of the Temple of Karabor) and several elite areas.\n\n=== Maps and subregions ===\n[[File:WorldMap-ShadowmoonValley.jpg|thumb|300px|left|Map of Shadowmoon Valley]]\n{| class=\"darktable\"\n|-\n!{{wow-inline}} In-game\n|-\n|{{Shadowmoon Valley|subzonesonly=}}\n|-\n| (WC2)\n|-\n| [[Skeletal Coast]]\n|}\n{{clrl}}\n<gallery>\nImage:Draenoractiii.jpg|Shadowmoon region prior to the destruction of Draenor.\nImage:Shadowmoonruins.JPG|Shadowmoon region as it may have appeared in Warcraft III.\n</gallery>\n\n=== Dungeons ===\n{| class=\"darktable\"\n! Dungeon Name \n! Level Range \n! Group Size\n! Approximate Run Time\n|-\n| {{portal|Black Temple|raid}}  || 70+\n| 25-man\n| Unknown\n|}\n\n=== Elite areas ===\n* [[Eclipsion Fields]]\n* [[Crimson Watch]]\n* [[The Path of Conquest]]\n* [[Ata'mal Terrace]]\n* [[Invasion Point: Cataclysm]]\n\n=== Travel hubs ===\n[[File:Ruins of Baa'ri.jpg|thumb|Ruins of Baa'ri]]\n;{{Alliance}} [[Wildhammer Stronghold]]\n\n;{{Horde}} [[Shadowmoon Village]]\n\n;{{factionIcon|Aldor|small}} [[Altar of Sha'tar]]\n\n;{{factionIcon|Scryers|Small}} [[Sanctum of the Stars]]\n\n=== Adjacent regions ===\n{| class=\"darktable\"\n|-\n! Zone Name || Faction || Level Range || Direction || Access\n|-\n| [[Terokkar Forest]]\n| {{Alliance Icon Small}}{{Horde Icon Small}}\n| 62-65 || West || Normal\n|}\n\n== Notable characters ==\n{{main|Shadowmoon Valley NPCs}}\n{{Stub/NPC}}\n*{{npc||Akama}}\n*{{npc||Maiev Shadowsong}}\n*{{npc||Teron Gorefiend}}\n*{{npc||Kurdran Wildhammer}} and {{npc||Sky'ree}}\n*{{npc||Zuluhed the Whacked}}\n\n== Quests ==\n{{main|Shadowmoon Valley quests}}\n{{Stub/Quest}}\n\n== Resources ==\n{{Stub/Other}}\n[[Herbs]]\n* {{item|Felweed}}\n* {{item|Nightmare Vine}}\n* {{item|Dreaming Glory}}\n* {{item|Terocone}}\n* {{item|Mana Thistle}}\n\n[[Leather]]\n* {{item|Crystal Infused Leather}}\n* {{item|Fel Scales}}\n* {{item|Knothide Leather}}\n* {{item|Knothide Leather Scraps}}\n\nMiscellaneous\n* [[Felmist]] - {{item|Mote of Shadow}} - Can only be harvested by [[engineers]]\n\n== Wild creatures ==\n<!-- Do not remove this DIV: it prevents the Wiki code from inserting an extra linebreak above this table. -->\n{| width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"table-layout:fixed;\"\n|- valign=\"top\"\n|\n* [[Air elemental]]s\n* [[Arakkoa|Arakkoa ghosts]]\n* [[Blood elves]]\n* [[Chimaera]]s\n* [[Colossi]]\n* [[Core hound]]s\n* [[Diemetradon]]s\n* [[Doomguard]]\n* [[Dragonhawk]]s\n* [[Drakonid]]s\n* [[Dreadlord]]s\n|\n* [[Earth elemental]]s\n* [[Elekk]]s\n* [[Eredar]]\n* [[Fel orc]]s\n* [[Fel reaver]]s\n* [[Felboar]]\n* [[Felguard]]s\n* [[Fire elemental]]\n* [[Fleshbeast]]s\n* [[Gan'arg]]\n* [[Ghost]]s\n|\n* [[Infernal]]s\n* [[Naga]]\n* [[Mo'arg]]\n* [[Nether dragon]]s\n* [[Nether drake]]s\n* [[Nether ray]]s\n* [[Ooze]]s\n* [[Owl]]s\n* [[Pit lord]]s\n* [[Ravager]]s\n* [[Rock flayer]]s\n|\n* [[Satyr]]\n* [[Scorpid]]s\n* [[Serpent]]s\n* [[Shadow Council]]\n* [[Shivarra]]\n* [[Succubi]]\n* [[Water elemental]]s\n* [[Wrathguard]]s\n|}\n\n== Notes ==\n*Traditional [[Mounts#Flying_mounts|flying mounts]] can be purchased at [[Wildhammer Stronghold]] for the [[Alliance]] and [[Shadowmoon Village]] for the [[Horde]]. The [[nether drake]]s are also purchased here from the [[Netherwing]] faction on [[Netherwing Ledge]]. Other places to purchase a flying mount include [[Blackwind Landing]] in [[Terokkar Forest]] from the [[Sha'tari Skyguard]] faction or [[Cenarion Refuge]] in [[Zangarmarsh]] from the [[Cenarion Expedition]] faction.\n*[http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DSTMYfQF-bg Video of Shadowmoon Valley]\n\n== External links ==\n{{elinks-zone|3520}}\n\n\n{{Shadowmoon Valley}}\n{{Outland}}\n\n[[es:Valle Sombraluna]]\n[[fr:Vall\u00e9e d'Ombrelune]]\n[[pl:Shadowmoon Valley]]\n[[ru:\u0414\u043e\u043b\u0438\u043d\u0430 \u041f\u0440\u0438\u0437\u0440\u0430\u0447\u043d\u043e\u0439 \u041b\u0443\u043d\u044b]]\n[[Category:Deserts]]\n[[Category:Outland]]\n[[Category:Shadowmoon Valley| ]]\n[[Category:Valleys]]"}}}